HEADWORD: Stultiloquence
<hw>Stul*til"o*quence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>stultiloquentia</ets>; <ets>stultus</ets> foolish +
<ets>loquentia</ets> a talking, fr. <ets>loquens</ets>, p. pr. of
<ets>loqui</ets> to talk.]</ety> <def>Silly talk; babbling.</def>⟦br⟧
